      "value": {
        "latex": "Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes {\\`a} un ordre\n    queclonque de $1-X^2$ par $1 - 2X\\cos\\theta + X^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes\n<span>à</span> un ordre queclonque de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(1-X^2\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 -\n2X\\cos\\theta + X^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9d806857-57bd-410d-b40c-43d0bc60b8eb",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$1-X^2 = (1-2X\\cos\\theta+X^2)(1 + 2X\\cos\\theta + \\dots + 2X^n\\cos n\\theta)\n                    + 2X^{n+1}\\cos(n+1)\\theta - 2X^{n+2}\\cos n\\theta$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1-X^2 = (1-2X\\cos\\theta+X^2)(1 +\n2X\\cos\\theta + \\dots + 2X^n\\cos n\\theta)\n                    + 2X^{n+1}\\cos(n+1)\\theta - 2X^{n+2}\\cos\nn\\theta\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7427a626-bc38-470a-a140-4b741ef350a9",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire la valeur de $1 + 2\\sum_{k=1}^n \\cos k\\theta$,\n    ($\\theta \\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\,{2\\pi})$).",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire la valeur de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 +\n2\\sum_{k=1}^n \\cos k\\theta\\)</span>, (<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\theta\n\\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\,{2\\pi})\\)</span>).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ca75ac31-d438-4776-8995-921d8662d9d8",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$=\\frac{\\cos n\\theta - \\cos(n+1)\\theta}{1-\\cos\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(=\\frac{\\cos n\\theta -\n\\cos(n+1)\\theta}{1-\\cos\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
